response.overview: i noticed the last video was very quiet so i tried to boost the audio in this one! still getting used to the audio effects in premiere. they're so much simpler than in ableton yet somehow so much more complicated to me. i might do a zelda collection video one of these days when i consolidate all my stuff, it's a bit scattered around my house at the moment.  all music in this video composed by koji kondo for the legend of zelda: ocarina of time soundtrack.
